WEBVTT

00:04:59.475 --> 00:05:03.841
It struck me that it would have
been strange anyway,

00:05:03.865 --> 00:05:06.245
for Jesus to come back again and again

00:05:06.269 --> 00:05:07.905
based on the different time zones.

00:05:07.929 --> 00:05:13.242
(Laughter)

00:05:15.037 --> 00:05:17.210
And this made me feel
even more ridiculous --

00:05:18.354 --> 00:05:19.555
hurt, really.

00:05:21.076 --> 00:05:24.245
But there on that night,
I did not stop believing.

00:05:25.197 --> 00:05:26.781
I just believed a new thing:

00:05:27.487 --> 00:05:29.919
that it was possible not to believe.